=== macOS privileged-helper RNUF reproduction (Gap I) ===
Run: 2026-05-25T23:26:15Z

The privileged-helper accepts the RNUF frame from the daemon but never
replies via SCM_RIGHTS, causing the daemon to hit EAGAIN on recvmsg
(socket has a read_timeout but never gets a reply). Verified by running
the helper standalone and probing via raw RNUF frame.

